    "causal_summary": "The model registry (`model-profiles.json`) and all historical benchmark run-data lived in multiple locations — primarily inside sk-prompt and across six spec sub-phase folders — creating fragmented, hard-to-maintain state. This work consolidates the registry into `sk-prompt-small-model/assets/`, moves all benchmark outputs to `sk-prompt-small-model/benchmarks/`, strips sk-prompt of every small-model reference so it becomes a generic forkable framework engine, and locks deep-improvement's model-benchmark command to write exclusively to the hub.",
